data.description:
Four bedroom 2.5 bath home on 5 acres and a pond.located in New Castle Va ( Craig Co) with beautiful mountain views. Country living with “in town” convenience. This one level living home has 2600 sq ft plus 1200 sq ft unfinished walkout basement and an open floor plan.
Kitchen has lots of storage with a gas cooktop and separate oven.
Gas fireplace upstairs and down.
Large primary bedroom suite with walk-in closet, soaking tub, and separate shower.
Large Trex deck and patio. Patio has fire pit, pergola, hot tub hook up and gas grill line installed. Ideal entertaining area.
Detached 27x48 garage with 2 room up and 2 rooms down. Separate electric service and heat pump. 19x24 covered dog kennel attached with heat/air access for dog houses.
Roof new in 2012, Heat pump, water heater, and well pump all new in the past 6 years.
House has a whole house generator to take the worry out of storms.
Located one mile from schools, grocery, doctor, and restaurants. Walking distance to hiking/bike trail and Craig Creek. Close by-Appalachian Trail Triple Crown- Dragon’s Tooth, McAfee Knob, and Tinker Cliffs.
Whether you are an outdoor enthusiast or just enjoy peace and tranquility this is the home for you!1
